OL,3,CHouseholds to receive up to #2,000
OL,4,Ccompensation for water service failures
OL,6,FWater firms will be forced to pay
OL,7,Fhouseholds in England up to #2,000 for
OL,8,Fservice failures as part of efforts to
OL,9,Freform the sector, the Government has
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FCompensation payments will increase up
OL,13,Fto tenfold from July 2 for problems
OL,14,Fsuch as low pressure, disruptions to
OL,15,Fsupply or sewer flooding.
