OL,6,FThe Department for Environment, Food
OL,7,Fand Rural Affairs (Defra) said the
OL,8,Fmove marked the first increase in
OL,9,Fcompensation rates in 25 years in
OL,10,Frecognition of the "urgent need" to
OL,11,Fbring payments in line with inflation
OL,12,Fand properly compensate households for
OL,13,Fpoor service.
