OL,4,Ccompensation for water service failures
OL,6,FSevere issues such as flooding will
OL,7,Fsee customer compensation double from
OL,8,F#1,000 to up to #2,000, while
OL,9,Fhouseholds suffering consistent low
OL,10,Fwater pressure will be automatically
OL,11,Feligible to receive up to #250, up
OL,12,Ffrom the previous compensation rate of
OL,13,F#25.
OL,15,FPayments will automatically be
OL,16,Fcredited to the accounts of eligible
OL,17,Fcustomers with immediate effect.
