OL,6,FThe announcement comes as the
OL,7,FGovernment attempts to grapple with
OL,8,Fthe problems engulfing the water
OL,9,Fsector in the face of high public
OL,10,Fanger over the degraded and polluted
OL,11,Fstate of rivers, lakes and coasts,
OL,12,Frising bills, bosses' bonuses and
OL,13,Fshareholder payouts.
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,16,F"Too many water companies are letting
OL,17,Fdown their customers ` with leaking
OL,18,Fpipes, poor water supply and low water
OL,19,Fpressure.
