OL,6,FMike Keil, the chief executive of the
OL,7,FConsumer Council for Water (CCW),
OL,8,Fsaid: "Customers expect to be treated
OL,9,Ffairly when their water company lets
OL,10,Fthem down, so we're delighted the
OL,11,FGovernment has moved at pace to
OL,12,Fstrengthen service standards.
OL,14,F"This should give people peace of mind
OL,15,Fthey now have far stronger protection
OL,16,Ffrom a much broader range of water
OL,17,Fcompany service failures ` from the
OL,18,Fslow installation of water meters to
OL,19,Fthe mishandling of debt recovery.
